The paper deals with signal analysis and image processing, specifically with the detection of blob-like features in noisy and compressed images. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes a measure for blob detection and a keypoint description, which involves mathematical derivations and computations, indicating that the paper may also belong to the information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and signal processing (cs.SI) sub-categories.
